The classes are GPTFaissIndex, GPTSimpleVectorIndex, GPTWeaviateIndex, GPTPineconeIndex, and GPTQdrantIndex. These classes are used to create and manage vector-based indices, and the __all__ variable is used to list all the classes for easy access. The purpose of this code is to provide a way to store and retrieve data using vector-based indices, allowing for efficient data storage and retrieval.
